Author: VentingFooligan6000
Text: I'm glad you think you're having a decent day, I don't think you're alone in having a brain that makes it seem like others are more hostile or distant or harsher than what it actually is in reality. Even if you see this day as a setback you can still benefit from the additional nutrients that you've missed out previously on and it could very well balance out in the end  Stay strong and safe
